  <data name="MissionTitle" xml:space="preserve"><value>Mission</value></data>
  <data name="GoalsTitle" xml:space="preserve"><value>Goals</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Promotion and education in the field of cryptocurrencies with a main focus on Bitcoin;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Creating a community of users, developers and enthusiasts of cryptocurrencies with a main focus on Bitcoin;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Providing information and advice on the legal and regulatory framework of cryptocurrencies and Bitcoin;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Uniting the interests of its members and supporting their development, qualification and knowledge;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_5" xml:space="preserve"><value>Stimulating dialogue and discussions, as well as creating an authoritative source of quality information;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_6" xml:space="preserve"><value>Uniting and attracting new members with similar interests;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_7" xml:space="preserve"><value>Promoting cooperation and contacts between members and the community;</value></data>
  <data name="Goals_8" xml:space="preserve"><value>Supporting and stimulating the adoption of Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies as a technological solution.</value></data>

  <data name="MeansTitle" xml:space="preserve"><value>Means</value></data>
  <data name="Means_1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Organizing meetings, conferences, seminars, webinars, educational courses, presentations and other similar events;</value></data>
  <data name="Means_2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Creating and distributing advertising materials in the media (press, television, Internet) with information about the Association's activities for fundraising and new members;</value></data>
  <data name="Means_3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Issuing information and educational materials on the topic of cryptocurrencies and Bitcoin;</value></data>
  <data name="Means_4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Conducting research and analysis in the field of cryptocurrencies and Bitcoin;</value></data>
  <data name="Means_5" xml:space="preserve"><value>Implementing and maintaining information exchange and relations with similar associations with similar interests in the country and abroad;</value></data>
  <data name="Means_6" xml:space="preserve"><value>Other activity, when the same is not prohibited by Law and related to the goals and means of the Association.</value></data>

